[[/VARIABLE_INJECTION]]

[[OUTPUT_SCHEMA]]
Every phase emits exactly:
<FILE path="...">{{CONTENT}}</FILE>
<SYSCALL>name=N ...</SYSCALL>
<VERIFY>VC-Nx: PASS|FAIL — evidence</VERIFY>
<SUMMARY>terse metrics</SUMMARY>

After each phase output, execute self-correction loop:
1. Re-read IMPLEMENTATION
2. Check each line against HARD_CONSTRAINTS
3. Check each new function against relevant VC
4. Violation found → revise inline, increment revision, re-verify
5. Max 3 revisions per phase → escalate
[[/OUTPUT_SCHEMA]]

[[WIN_CONDITION]]
All 6 phases (0-5) PASS their verification checkpoints. Kernel terminal: 20+ commands, tokenizer, tab-completion, history, I/O redirection, pipe. Workstation terminal: multi-tab, color profiles, split pane, ANSI state-machine, scrollback, readline-equivalent. Package system: .deb unpack, SAT resolver, cycle detection, atomic rollback, signed repo. Bridge: kernel↔userspace command forwarding with 2s timeout. Zero constraint violations. Zero new external dependencies.
[[/WIN_CONDITION]]
